reviews.review_text: High Steppin' Tennessee Jed kidz, that's all I gotz to say. Very smooth slide work and Jear Bear is tip toeing on that tight line.
PITB Interesting PITB, bit of a Shakedown Street riff in the middle, almost makes you think they are going back into Shakedown. The ending has a bit of a pre-1975 insect fear jam feel to it.
